Salary: McEasy provides Internet-based and GPS-based digital solutions to address the needs of logistics operations and vehicle location tracking. Our company was founded in 2017 and continues to transform to become a leader in providing integrated solutions in the field of logistics transportation and warehousing. As a software company, we will always conduct product research and development regularly so that it can be relied upon for our loyal customers Our company uses advanced technology in our software products, such as object-oriented design and programming languages for fast and stable performance. With VSMS & TMS as an integrated vehicle logistics service with a digital-based subscription system in your company, through an online system that we have built and tested, you can track the vehicle's position in real-time and all operational costs transparently, without the hassle of checking them manually. On July, McEasy secured USD 6.5 million (approximately IDR 97 billion) in a series A round headed by East Ventures, which increased its initial USD 1,5 million investment. Hundreds of companies use our product to assist their operations and logistics, including Alfamidi, FedEx, Club, MGM Bosco, PO Rosalia Indah, Mulia Ceramics, Polda Jatim, Go Trans, and AKAS.
